msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga"
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Bahudhītarasutta → bahudhītusuttaṃ (bj, pts2) | bahudhitisuttaṃ (si, s2, s3) | bahudhītisuttaṃ (s1) | bahudhīti (pts1)
msgctxt "sn7.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Bahudhītarasutta"
msgstr "10. Many Daughters"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.365"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans in a certain forest grove."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa catuddasa balībaddā naṭṭhā honti."
msgstr "Now at that time one of the brahmins of the Bhāradvāja clan had lost fourteen oxen."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo te balībadde gavesanto yena so vanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā addasa bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr "While looking for them he went to that forest, where he saw the Buddha sitting down cross-legged, with his body straight, and mindfulness established right there."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.4"
msgid "Disvāna yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr "He went up to the Buddha, and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
